@baseUrl = http://localhost:8888
@authToken = your_jwt_token_here
@billId = 1
@customerId = 1

### List all bills
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bills
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Generate a postpaid bill from a meter reading
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bills/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meterReadingId": 1,
  "dueDate": "2026-06-25"
}

### Get a bill by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bills/{{billId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### View my own bills (ROLE_CUSTOMER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bills/me
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### List bills for a customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bills/customer/{{customerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Approve a bill (ROLE_ADMIN / ROLE_FINANCE)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/bills/{{billId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}